name: EmitWarningOptions
summary: An abstract type for the options that may be passed to emitWarning().

properties.name: code
properties.summary: A unique identifier for the warning instance being emitted.

properties.name: ctor
properties.summary: When warning is a String, ctor is an optional function used to limit the generated stack trace.

properties.name: detail
properties.summary: Additional text to include with the error.

properties.name: type
properties.summary: When warning is a String, type is the name to use for the type of warning being emitted.
